{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_08_03",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 3話 お年玉のお礼も兼ねて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お年玉が、ほしいです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "New Year’s money… please…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ、琴乃。言えないなら言えないでいいんだ\n無理にごまかさなくていいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Kotono. If it’s hard to say‚ it’s okay.\nYou don’t have to force yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ～……本当なんです……\n月ストの旅行に使うお金が足りなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I'm telling the truth…\nI don’t have enough money for the Moon Tempest trip…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　ほ、本当に？\nお年玉がほしいって……それだけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? R-really?\nYou need New Year’s money…? That’s all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.5333342234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "追い打ちをかけないで下さい！　うぅぅ～……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t corner me! Ughhh~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333342234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.8333342234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない。そうか、うん、なるほどな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry. I see‚ yeah‚ I understand.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.8333342234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5333339691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "うぅぅ～……恥ずかしいし\nみんなに申し訳ないです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ughhh… This is so embarrassing…\nand I’m so sorry for making everyone worry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2666673024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "「お年玉がほしい」って一言言うだけで良かったのに\nみんなに心配かけて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could’ve just said‚ “New Year’s money‚ please?”\nbut instead‚ I made everyone worry…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0666662853,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8000026704
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "私もすずや芽衣みたいに\nストレートに言えたら良かったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like Suzu and Mei…\nI wish I could’ve been as straightforward as them…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9333360037,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "すずはもう少し遠慮してほしいくらいだけどな\nそれじゃあ、はい。お年玉",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish Suzu would be a bit more reserved‚ though.\nWell then‚ here. Your New Year’s money.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333385469,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cloth-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5099.994786500005,
          "startTime": 64.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cloth-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5905.633760100002,
          "startTime": 69.138972307
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.4000062308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いいん、ですか……？\nえ……ちゃんとポチ袋に入ってる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is it… okay…?\nEh… It’s even in an envelope…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3333395642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.8333395642
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "元々みんなに渡すつもりだったんだよ\nでも、琴乃に渡すタイミングを逃してたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was originally planning on giving everyone some.\nBut I missed the chance to give you yours‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.8666728975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.1666728975
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、カフェで渡そうとしてくれてたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Were you going to give it to me at the cafe?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666728975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。その後うっかり忘れてたんだ、すまない\nこれからは遠慮なんてしなくていいからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I accidentally forgot about it after that‚ sorry.\nYou don’t have to be so reserved from now on‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.9333293917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 92.6999960584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……ございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6999960584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.7333253226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "うぅ……私、本当に何してたんでしょう\nここ最近ずっとお年玉のことばっかり",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… What have I been doing…\nAll I’ve been thinking about lately is New Year’s money…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6999919893,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 107.0333268485
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "こんな煩悩だらけじゃ……あ、そうだ\n旅行の時に、お寺で座禅を体験すれば……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m so full of worldly desires… Ah‚ that’s right.\nMaybe I should try zen meditation at a temple during the trip…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9999935152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "精神修行にはいいかもな\nすずとか、ずっと叩かれてそうだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be good for mental training.\nSuzu would probably get scolded the whole time‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3999904635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――グラビア撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――On the day of the gravure shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7333192192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.8666454318
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.8666454318
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.9999787651
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "よく似合ってるな、琴乃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks good on you‚ Kotono.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.8666454318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.3333120985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nこの衣装を着るのは久しぶりですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nIt’s been a while since I wore this outfit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.5333120985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今日は随分とすっきりした顔をしてるが\n何かいいことがあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem cheerful today.\nDid something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.0999787651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 139.3666454318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "心配事が……なくなったからだと思います\nそれに、この衣装を着ると、いろいろ思い出して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it’s because… my worries are gone.\nAnd wearing this outfit… brings me back so many memories…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.0666454318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 149.46664238
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "月ストメンバーの中でいろんな誤解が重なって\n寮が大変なことになったことがあったじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you remember when all those misunderstandings piled up between the Moon Tempest members‚\nand the dorm became a complete mess?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.26664238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "猫が逃げたり、すずがダイイングメッセージみたい\nなのを書いて倒れてたり……いろいろと凄かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cat ran away‚ Suzu collapsed after writing\nwhat looked like a dying message… That was wild.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.7666474663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "お正月から、寮の中であんなことが\n起きるなんて思いませんでしたよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I never thought that would happen in the dorm\nright after the new year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.0666362765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "shrine-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.5999696098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
