      "text": "本当にな。……お、そろそろ撮影が始まりそうだな\n今日の流れは頭に入ってるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s true… Oh‚ it looks like the shoot is about to start.\nDo you get the flow of today's schedule?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.8333029432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
