      "text": "インタビューを受けて、それから撮影をする……\nという流れですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We do the interview‚ and then the shoot…\nThat's the flow‚ Right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.5333029432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
