      "text": "星見市にいた頃の思い出話も聞かれるみたいなので\nさっきの話もちょっとだけ喋ってみますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like they’re going to ask about memories of when we were in Hoshimi City‚\nso I’ll talk a little about what happened earlier.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 188.576035375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね、この衣装を着ると\nとても懐かしい気持ちになります",
