      "startTime": 198.7332948051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "あの頃はまだ、NEXT VENUSグランプリで\n優勝したばかりで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ we had just won\nthe NEXT VENUS Grand Prix…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 204.6999757133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "一気にお仕事が増えて、嬉しいけどそれ以上に\n毎日戸惑ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The amount of work suddenly increased. I was happy‚ but\nmore than that‚ I was confused every day.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 211.56664238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "その忙しさにもだんだんと慣れて、東京に拠点を\n移して、それからもいろんなことがあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I gradually got used to the busy schedule‚ moved our base to Tokyo‚\nand even after that‚ a lot of things happened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.666646449,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "こうして今も活動出来ているのはファンの\nみなさんのおかげだなって、改めて感じます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m grateful that I’m still able to continue my activities like this‚\nthanks to all the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.6666444144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "今年の抱負、ですか？ そうですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year’s goals? Let’s see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 231.1666372937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなと一緒に、ライブにお仕事に\n充実したいい一年にしていきたいと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to have a fulfilling year with all the Moon Tempest members‚\nfilled with live shows and work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 242.1000132243,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5166.631190099992,
          "startTime": 247.2666444144
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
