      "startTime": 286.5333049776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "家内安全に縁結び……って\nこれは本当に俺用のお守りでいいのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A prayer for \"household safety\" and \"good relationships\"… Wait‚\nare these really good luck charms for me?",
        "id": ""
