      },
      "startTime": 300.6000082654,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_08_03-ktn030.m4a",
      "text": "あとは、縁結びはお仕事の良縁に恵まれます\nように、って意味です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And \"good relationships\" is for being blessed\nwith good work relationships.",
